<html><head><title>Halloween Happenings</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>Halloween Happenings</h3><p>It's official ...<br><br>EverQuest® II: Nights of the Dead only comes once a year in Norrath, so players take heed!<br><br>During this ghastly holiday, citizens of Norrath can venture into Qeynos or Freeport to free the spirits trapped in the haunted houses, combat evil in the haunted mansion missions, trick-or-treat with NPC’s in the cities for something especially sweet or participate in Ponchy the Halfling’s petrifying quest series!<br><br>Nights of the Dead is scheduled to run Oct. 22 through Nov. 3.</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Wednesday, 15 Oct, 2008<br>Link: <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=46302">http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=46302</a><br>Printed On: Sat Aug 25 0:13:07 PDT 2012<br>©2008 IGN Entertainment</font></span>